  "text": "Of course, the analogous formula holds for rk( HF (−Σ(B n − ,2 ))). Moreover, since B u n − ,2 = B u n − ,0 is alternating, we know from [CITATION_1] that rk( HF (−Σ(B u n − ,2 ))) = det(B u n − ,0 ). And, since B n − ,0 is an alternating link, its determinant satisfies",
